{"tid":1141813,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文求教] 22歲 fresh grad 輸錢番唔到轉頭 覺得自己好對唔住屋企","createTime":"2019-05-06T17:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T03:22:10.000Z","uid":165208,"like":2,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6e877b48068536a7822970768553dd2887e676a2","tid":1141813,"uid":165208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:14:35.000Z","msg":"今年grad 22 出黎做左半年野到 但最近過大海賭錢 至今輸左成700蚊 <br />\n<br />\n畢業諗住搵下外快 出糧之後就同咗朋友過大海 <br />\n<br />\n我都唔明自己點解要賭 好想羸好想要錢 好想報答返屋企人 <br />\n<br />\n咩遊戲我都玩 全部 10蚊 平住推 睇下可唔可以連贏10round 即走人<br />\n<br />\n睇下可唔可以 10蚊變二百萬 <br />\n<br />\n通頂十幾個鍾一路係咁輸 試過連輸8 round<br />\n<br />\n最後真係頂唔順 直接坐船番香港<br />\n<br />\n坐下船番香港果陣女朋友瘋狂WHATAPPS 我 問我成晚去左邊 我係船到流左兩下眼淚<br />\n<br />\n我宜家真係唔唔知點算 覺得自己好對唔住屋企<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QAwVgUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQAwVgUs.jpg&h=66592442&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9ce371908e1e1c49cd3b9003e02d68ea5a58d1f","tid":1141813,"uid":244867,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"師兄唔借多700番身？"},{"pid":"243a7d2256521c93ca620b1f06afd0235861a93c","tid":1141813,"uid":180707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:21:45.000Z","msg":"買咗700牛？"},{"pid":"d2152ca80467c57a9ee3453db4603f96f889268f","tid":1141813,"uid":5375,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"700蚊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賭場影相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0410d315cb6b9fa97acef42105e088aa5abf0d","tid":1141813,"uid":91507,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"0/10<br />\n建議十蚊改做一千蚊 七百改成七萬 投入感更強"},{"pid":"6bae7d5a62c3314a5b63ca4f0934b2bb8ae19a97","tid":1141813,"uid":243435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T18:02:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd9078cc3591f8dcd010ac47161ff6f3189c5aae","tid":1141813,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T18:24:10.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3d3c8b22ebd212bf15b519d4a3d2301d09b2a9","tid":1141813,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T21:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d214f283f64f8b9c9fe383fcfba7fb710603e00","tid":1141813,"uid":2590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T21:03:02.000Z","msg":"好似真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7575eb4d9fd3a907293741eeaf7f4b2198458a6","tid":1141813,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"至今輸左成700蚊 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdddcb4bd1f107f71d631ba816d5fe58296ac2a3","tid":1141813,"uid":35580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:48:31.000Z","msg":"咸左"},{"pid":"41a7938ccca4e646763ffbc641dd4e2717b0608c","tid":1141813,"uid":213142,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"賭場影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快有人會搵到樓主，做定心理準備"},{"pid":"6928f2bfb51e4181e99e2a7d4663022387ecbbb1","tid":1141813,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd9078cc3591f8dcd010ac47161ff6f318